<h2>Bottom Line</h2>
<p><strong>Start with Apollo</strong> if you're an individual SDR or small team that needs to be productive immediately. It covers 80% of what most outbound reps need in a single tool at a reasonable price.</p>
<p><strong>Add Clay</strong> when you've hit Apollo's ceiling — typically when you're running 1,000+ leads/month and data accuracy or personalization depth is limiting your reply rates. Clay is not a replacement for Apollo; it's the upgrade layer on top of it.</p>

